               Governor's Office for Innovation in Government

                               Innovation-Gram

   Regular bulletin intended to keep state change agents abreast of
   significant activities going on in the Governor's Office for Innovation
   in Government, as well as to highlight innovative happenings around the
   state and around the world that might have an impact on today's
   workplace.

   The publications listed below are available in Adobe Acrobat PDF
   format. Viewing PDF documents requires Acrobat Reader, available as a
   free download from Adobe Systems.
     * January 2002 Innovation-Gram
       Highlights: Executive Leadership Forum on information security,
       reports on the "Clarity Award," "Public Service Excellence Award,"
       tips for coping with bureaucracy and this year's winners of the
       California Awards for Performance Excellence.

   2001 Innovation-Grams



